2019-02-27 21:20:22.864 +08:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@__id_0='?' (Size = 450)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [x.Claims].[Id], [x.Claims].[ClaimType], [x.Claims].[ClaimValue], [x.Claims].[UserId]
FROM [AspNetUserClaims] AS [x.Claims]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT TOP(1) [x0].[Id]
    FROM [AspNetUsers] AS [x0]
    WHERE [x0].[Id] = @__id_0
    ORDER BY [x0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [x.Claims].[UserId] = [t].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Id]

FROM [AspNetUserClaims] AS [x.Claims]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT TOP(1) [x0].[Id]
    FROM [AspNetUsers] AS [x0]
    WHERE [x0].[Id] = @__id_0

) AS [t] ON [x.Claims].[UserId] = [t].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Id]
